These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
House: tower, art-deco, craftsman, wooden
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, siglo, alhambra, old-henry
1. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
2. the art-deco house is not the swisher-smoker##6
3. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the craftsman house is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the tower house is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
6. the swisher-smoker is not the craftsman house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | art-deco   | wooden    | tower    | craftsman |
| Sport      | old-henry | swisher | alhambra | siglo |

