.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, dutch, malaysian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, amaryllis, dahlia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
3. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
4. the colombian is not the person who growspoppy##6
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the malaysian is on the right of the chinese##1
8. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | colombian  | dutch    | chinese | malaysian    |
| Food       | dahlia | poppy | amaryllis  | zinnia |

