.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, january, november, july
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, tiparillo, chaman, vegafina
1. the person who's birthday is in july is not the cain-smoker##6
2. the tiparillo-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
3. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
4. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
7. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
8. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | july       | january  | october  | november |
| Job        | chaman | vegafina | tiparillo | cain  |

