.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different games are played: bridge, whist, billiard, snooker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, soul, country, salsa
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
3. the fan salsa is not the person playing whist##6
4. the fan salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan punk##5
5. the fan country is on the right of the fan soul##1
6. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the fan salsa##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | whist | billiard | snooker     | bridge |
| Transport   | soul     | country    | punk | salsa    |

