.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, pall-mall, baccarat, dannemann
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, pepper, lime, carrot
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating lime##5
3. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating pepper##5
4. the pall-mall-smoker is not the person eating carrot##6
5. the person eating strawberry is not the montecristo-smoker##6
6. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
7. the person eating lime is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | montecristo        | dannemann | baccarat | pall-mall |
| Transport   | carrot | strawberry | pepper     | lime   |

