.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, analyst, chef, writer
City: venice, hannover, new-york, paris
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the designer##1
2. the writer is not the person traveling to hannover##6
3. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
5. the chef is the chef##1
6. the chef is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
7. the chef is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
8. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
9. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | analyst | chef    | designer  | writer   |
| Nationality   | new-york  | paris | hannover | venice |

