.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, peach, corn, zucchini
4 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, fish, ferret
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
6. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
7. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
8. the person eating peach is not the owner of the ferret##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | peach  | watermelon        | corn      | zucchini          |
| Job        | snake | rabbit | ferret | fish |

