.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, zucchini, corn, mango
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, fuchsia, aquamarine, black
1. the person who likes white is not the person eating tomato##6
2. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person who likes black is the person who likes black##1
4. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who likes black##1
5. the person eating corn is not the person who likes black##6
6. the person who likes fuchsia is not the person eating zucchini##6
7. the person who likes black is in an even position##4
8. the person eating corn is the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | corn | tomato        | mango  | zucchini     |
| Sport   | white     | black | fuchsia | aquamarine |

