House: victorian, modern, gothic-revival, cape-cod
1. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
2. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
3. the gothic-revival house is not the person who likes green##6
4. the person who likes amber is between the cape-cod house and the person who likes green##2
5. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
6. the modern house is between the victorian house and the person who likes white##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | green | amber    | white | chestnut |
| Music-Genre   | victorian         | modern | cape-cod   | gothic-revival     |

