4. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
5. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the roller and the person drinking sprite##2
6. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | bike | roller      | bus | helicopter   |
| Movie-Genre   | tea     | almond-milk | soy-milk   | sprite |

