.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, aquamarine, orange, blue
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, horse, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
2. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is not the person who likes turquise##6
5. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
6. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | turquise | aquamarine | blue      | orange   |
| Transport   | chinchilla  | ferret   | horse | rabbit |

 